  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Outline</h2>This game is a casual game with simple controls that combines puzzle elements with run and jump elements.<br>Place blocks to make a path, and align blocks vertically while breaking walls,Use monsters and blocks to get in the way of the brave heroes and reach the goal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Summary</h2>The main character is a still immature, cute (kawaii) Devil.<br>The Devil attacks a town, but is beaten back by the heroes.<br>The Devil uses her power to manipulate the blocks to create a path,She turns back and escapes along the road that he herself has destroyed.<br><br>This is the story of the escape of a dumb and cute (kawaii) Devil who was defeated by the heroes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Game Rules</h2>Run away to the goal before the heroes catch up with you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Operation Methods</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/6ffc3b63b7f4d1f8ec2b08c4feb8f859.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/6ffc3b63b7f4d1f8ec2b08c4feb8f859.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/6ffc3b63b7f4d1f8ec2b08c4feb8f859.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Mouse operation</strong><br>・Drag and drop to place blocks (monsters)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/eb25046db0bf9e803e40d69937c31664.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/eb25046db0bf9e803e40d69937c31664.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/eb25046db0bf9e803e40d69937c31664.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Xbox Controller Controls</strong><br>・Cross key or stick: Move where you want to place<br>・A: Place a block (monster)<br>・X: Select a monster<br>・LB/RB: Toggle block selection (shortcut function)<br>・B/LT/RT: Move the placement location (shortcut function)<br><strong>DUALSHOCK (DualSense) controller controls</strong><br>・Cross key or stick: Move where you want to place<br>・×: Place a block (monster)<br>・□: Select a monster<br>・L1/R1: Toggle block selection (shortcut function)<br>・○/L2/R2: Move the placement location (shortcut function)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Techniques</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/c6ff14aa5131b267e59c4ca8cbcac876.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/c6ff14aa5131b267e59c4ca8cbcac876.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/c6ff14aa5131b267e59c4ca8cbcac876.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>・Blocks can be erased by aligning them vertically<br>　(At the same time, it grants a fixed time reduction in movement speed to the hero)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/5b9d38981f88ed5fc777a7297a566ae6.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/5b9d38981f88ed5fc777a7297a566ae6.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/5b9d38981f88ed5fc777a7297a566ae6.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>・You can block the hero by placing blocks behind the Devil<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/0d0409717e301f7967bbd112b169ae5b.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/0d0409717e301f7967bbd112b169ae5b.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/0d0409717e301f7967bbd112b169ae5b.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>・Score according to the number of blocks when you place a block<br>・When you place a block adjacent to an already existing block, you can get a combo score<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Gimmicks</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/cca4dcb6f501f8750abc7c861c26019a.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/cca4dcb6f501f8750abc7c861c26019a.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/cca4dcb6f501f8750abc7c861c26019a.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>・Meat: Movement speed increases for a certain period of time and score points<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/e574b2841ccbfa6ff33ed2a385d64fc1.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/e574b2841ccbfa6ff33ed2a385d64fc1.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/e574b2841ccbfa6ff33ed2a385d64fc1.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/fb71bed367cd91ae2cbf1c61af5e67a1.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/fb71bed367cd91ae2cbf1c61af5e67a1.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/fb71bed367cd91ae2cbf1c61af5e67a1.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/33ab7691948eda2dd8956f25941417f8.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/33ab7691948eda2dd8956f25941417f8.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/33ab7691948eda2dd8956f25941417f8.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/67d047980700510e7a7f8d4742fe3227.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/67d047980700510e7a7f8d4742fe3227.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/67d047980700510e7a7f8d4742fe3227.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>・Egg: Gains monsters that can be placed<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/42ce7e3105614064f17d878606c445d6.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/42ce7e3105614064f17d878606c445d6.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/42ce7e3105614064f17d878606c445d6.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>・Poisoned meat: Movement speed is reduced for a certain period of time<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/9468f7154f717ce8c6728f1ff38d949b.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=64 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/9468f7154f717ce8c6728f1ff38d949b.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/9468f7154f717ce8c6728f1ff38d949b.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>・Spikes: Game over immediately upon contact<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Character Introduction</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/d594702b6b5668057b5e3edd0f3d36cd.avif?t=1753166073\" width=256 height=256 /></span><br><strong>【The Devil】</strong><br>・The main character of this game<br>・He has the ability to destroy and create, to place and break blocks<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/242ad31fd72c255679a2241c5b5fc9f9.avif?t=1753166073\" width=128 height=128 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/3a624ab4a7bfa877018f2dce22e84eef.avif?t=1753166073\" width=128 height=128 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/02768c342b0e92f86aaa92c6c0777f6f.avif?t=1753166073\" width=128 height=128 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/e709eb9b990553ff8a24e34a7c79a3f9.avif?t=1753166073\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><strong>【Monsters】</strong><br>・The support of this game<br>・They interfere with the heroes and assist the Devil<br>・Monster (rock): Punches quickly, dealing small damage to the enemy<br>・Monster (flower): Increases the movement speed of the Demon King with a magical light<br>・Monster (mushroom): Spores reduce enemy movement speed for a certain period of time<br>・Monster (chicken): Explodes in a timed explosion, inflicting heavy damage on the enemy<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/45443100e9118dd5b963ee3502874355.avif?t=1753166073\" width=128 height=128 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/5c1fe7554a0fb6597a4d672df46b813b.avif?t=1753166073\" width=128 height=128 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/b3d4729fdcfe2294ea1bff4b056508b9.avif?t=1753166073\" width=128 height=128 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/f5eae44951f44f2201eb0269c12e4d23.avif?t=1753166073\" width=128 height=128 /></span><br><strong>【Hero】</strong><br>・Enemy of this game<br>・Hero of the Sword: Standard ability<br>・Hero of the Spear: Highly durable (not good at moving steps)<br>・Hero of the Magic: Fast on steps (not so good at walking)<br>・Hero of the Club: has high mobility (low durability)",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Outline</h2>This game is a casual game with simple controls that combines puzzle elements with run and jump elements.<br>Place blocks to make a path, and align blocks vertically while breaking walls,Use monsters and blocks to get in the way of the brave heroes and reach the goal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Summary</h2>The main character is a still immature, cute (kawaii) Devil.<br>The Devil attacks a town, but is beaten back by the heroes.<br>The Devil uses her power to manipulate the blocks to create a path,She turns back and escapes along the road that he herself has destroyed.<br><br>This is the story of the escape of a dumb and cute (kawaii) Devil who was defeated by the heroes.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Game Rules</h2>Run away to the goal before the heroes catch up with you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Operation Methods</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/6ffc3b63b7f4d1f8ec2b08c4feb8f859.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/6ffc3b63b7f4d1f8ec2b08c4feb8f859.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/6ffc3b63b7f4d1f8ec2b08c4feb8f859.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Mouse operation</strong><br>・Drag and drop to place blocks (monsters)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/eb25046db0bf9e803e40d69937c31664.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/eb25046db0bf9e803e40d69937c31664.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/eb25046db0bf9e803e40d69937c31664.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Xbox Controller Controls</strong><br>・Cross key or stick: Move where you want to place<br>・A: Place a block (monster)<br>・X: Select a monster<br>・LB/RB: Toggle block selection (shortcut function)<br>・B/LT/RT: Move the placement location (shortcut function)<br><strong>DUALSHOCK (DualSense) controller controls</strong><br>・Cross key or stick: Move where you want to place<br>・×: Place a block (monster)<br>・□: Select a monster<br>・L1/R1: Toggle block selection (shortcut function)<br>・○/L2/R2: Move the placement location (shortcut function)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >■Techniques</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/c6ff14aa5131b267e59c4ca8cbcac876.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/c6ff14aa5131b267e59c4ca8cbcac876.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/c6ff14aa5131b267e59c4ca8cbcac876.mp4?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>・Blocks can be erased by aligning them vertically<br>　(At the same time, it grants a fixed time reduction in movement speed to the hero)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/5b9d38981f88ed5fc777a7297a566ae6.poster.avif?t=1753166073\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945270/extras/5b9d38981f88ed5fc777a7297a566ae6.webm?t=1753166073\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source 